race.comment: WHISKY NINJA (1) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 400m behind Field Of Angels (23.30) in a Grade 5. Boasts a strong record from this draw with six wins and two minor placings from 12 starts. Key runner on her best form. PAW URSULA (2) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Ballarat over 450m behind Pretty Capri (26.40) in a Grade 5. Key runner on best form. ROMAN EMPIRE (6) comes off an average performance last start when seventh at Sale over 435m behind Akina Jazz (25.50) in a Grade 5. One of the better chances. SKY HIGH DREAMS (7) is a last-start placegetter who should be thereabouts.
